creator: Pints
descriptionHtml:
Start your stock investing journey with Pints - a social investing app that allows you to learn and trade stocks securely while having fun with your friends. It’s simple, secure, and free!

Say goodbye to complicated investing graphs and welcome a brand new interface that provides only the necessary tools for beginners. Created by a team of experts, Pints offers a social community of financial advisors to help you make smart choices. Whether you’re just starting out or have some experience, Pints is the app for you to take the first step into the world of investing.

Why Pints?
Simplicity & Security
We offer fractionalized shares for as low as $10 per trade
Simplified account opening & money management process
Build-Test-Operate model – back-test your Pint stocks and allocations
You own the assets you buy
Secure custody with SEC/SIPC approved broker and insured up to $250k per user
Curation & Creation
Choose your investments of your favourite stocks
Mix-Match stocks to create a blended portfolio
Copy Pints that you like or choose from any Pint created by certified experts
Managed & Mitigated Risks
Access to only 800+ stocks – no options or leveraged trading
Most liquid stocks, with the highest market cap
Content created to help guide you through your investing journey

With Pints, you can invest with confidence – and have a little fun while you’re at it.
